      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and feels as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed weekly, preserving its flawless original paint which retains a deep, mirror-like luster. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather seats remain supple and free of any wear, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented at every interval. Every button, switch, and feature functions perfectly, and the engine bay is incredibly clean. There are absolutely no dings, scratches, or curb rash on the wheels. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or driver to own a specimen in unparalleled condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
